column1: EIA data, but copied and redated to match Clack data.
Clack data goes from 1 Jan 2006 to 31 Dec 2008.  2008 is a leap year.
EIA data for full years goes from 1 Jan 2016 to 31 Dec 2017. 2016 is a leap year
To match 3 years of clack 2017 is mapped to 2006 and 2007, 2016 is mapped to 2008. Then these 3 years are normalize to a time mean of 1.
Lines above 'BEGIN_DATA' in the first column are for comment only.
